description: Luxury high-floor 1 bedroom, 1.5 bathrooms residence on the 71st floor of Trump Tower, offering breathtaking panoramic views of the lake and city skyline through soaring 11' floor-to-ceiling windows. This impeccably designed home features top-of-the-line finishes throughout, including Wolf, Sub-Zero, and Miele stainless steel appliances in the gourmet kitchen. The spacious primary suite boasts a large walk-in closet and a luxurious limestone bath with dual vanities, soaking tub, and separate glass-enclosed shower. Residents enjoy full access to Trump's world-class 5-star amenities including a state-of-the-art fitness center, spa, concierge, and more.
